=head1 DESCRIPTION

The wrapper that contains the Audit Manager role information of the
current user. This includes the role type and IAM Amazon Resource Name
(ARN).

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RoleArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RoleType => Str

The type of customer persona.

In C<CreateAssessment>, C<roleType> can only be C<PROCESS_OWNER>.

In C<UpdateSettings>, C<roleType> can only be C<PROCESS_OWNER>.

In C<BatchCreateDelegationByAssessment>, C<roleType> can only be
C<RESOURCE_OWNER>.



